Performs negacyclic forward and inverse number-theoretic transform (NTT), commonly used in RLWE cryptography.

detaileddescription.para: The number-theoretic transform (NTT) specializes the discrete Fourier transform (DFT) to the finite field $ \mathbb{Z}_q[X] / (X^N + 1) $.
